description: Deletes an Amazon Textract adapter version. Requires that you specify both an AdapterId and a AdapterVersion. Deletes the adapter version specified by the AdapterId and the AdapterVersion.

parameters.name: AdapterId
parameters.description: A string containing a unique ID for the adapter version that will be deleted.

parameters.name: AdapterVersion
parameters.description: Specifies the adapter version to be deleted.
